# PlateBlur - Automatic License Plate Blurring with YOLOv5

A Python tool for automatically detecting and blurring license plates in images using YOLOv5.

---

## Features

- Automatic license plate detection using YOLOv5
- Gaussian blur applied only to detected regions
- Local execution (no cloud required)
- Simple command-line interface
- Reproducible environment with pinned dependencies

